Lab: User role controlled by request parameter

Vulnerability: Admin Panel which identifies administrators using a forgeable cookie

Objective: Access admin panel and using it delete the user carlos

Exploitation Steps:
1. Connect Burp Suite with the lab on browser
2. Add the payload /admin into the url, these will show an error message.
3. In Burp Proxy, look for this request in http history and send it to the Repeater
